{"tid":606451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[智障劫匪] 中環珠寶劫案 警再拘兩疑犯","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T13:24:16.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bce6a9d67a5db93631949d8e0f6578a6af1c8c1b","tid":606451,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"中環威靈頓街珠寶店「聚寶珠寶」劫案，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警方晚上在深圳灣口岸，再拘捕多兩名哥倫比亞籍男子，懷疑他們準備潛逃到內地</strong></span>，連同早前拘捕的一人，至今有3人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發於早上約10時，3名賊人用鐵鎚打爛店舖飾櫃，再劫走約值4000萬元的財物。賊人犯案後往蘭桂坊方向逃去，其中一人被衝鋒隊員截獲扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n省港旗兵個年代都唔會係關口潛逃返鄰國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ae9c35978713bb533e27704e25bed204bffe86","tid":606451,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}